channel.title: Weird Error - Rep++
channel.description:
Hello Everyone,
I added a command today, and went to compile my server, when I randomly got a strange error out of no where.
I found a backup of my server, and compiled it to make sure it worked, and it worked fine.
I moved the file that was causing the problem to the recycle bin, and added the cleanly copiling version, but I still get the same error, what is wrong?
Thanks
